# beatadjoint depends on fenics, in particular dolfin (sudo apt-get
# install fenics) and dolfin-adjoint (launchpad.net/dolfin-adjoint)



# beatadjoint can be installed as any other Python module using
# distutils:

# For system-wise install do:

  sudo python setup.py install

# Or specify a local path:

  python setup.py install --prefix=/home/me/favorite-path
